    - NO-SQL -> Schema less, sharded by default, Json Modeling



* A database transaction is a group of database operations that must be treated as a single unit:
either all operations succeed, or all are undone.

* SELECT can be part of a transaction, but a SELECT statement alone is not necessarily what we mean by a transaction
